      "Title": "EngineeringUnits.EnergyPerArea",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/EngineeringUnits.EnergyPerArea.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Energy per unit area (e.g. fracture toughness E/A, surface energy).\nSI base unit: joule per square meter (J/m²). Dimensionally equal to\n<xref href=\"EngineeringUnits.SurfaceTension\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> (M/T²) but semantically distinct — kept\nseparate for the same reason <xref href=\"EngineeringUnits.Torque\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and <xref href=\"EngineeringUnits.Energy\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nare separate despite sharing M·L²/T².</p>\n"
